{
  "stem": "13851.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I guess it was just the beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we were allowed to stay.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they wanted [INAUDIBLE] before they took us to work, they need some for cleaning street of snow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went after the Jewish people, the young ones, to get us out in-- And at that times, they were hitting, and-- you know, and made you work, and screaming.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it felt terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the start of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He were not allowed to any do-- go any selling, doing anything, no.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was not allowed to go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So only thing-- they gave us rations, piece of bread, a certain bread of certain amount.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember we had to stay in the back of the long lines to get the bread for the family.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This 19-- the war started in 1939.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was continuing in the '40s, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, then there's-- they started-- it was not a yellow star.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had armband, a blue-- a white armband with blue stripes, and a star of David was on the side.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so that they knew exactly what-- who we are.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, I was about 14, 15.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was warning everyday, find somebody, Jewish people or Jewish kids without their band-- they will be killed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They knew that they already-- they're, like, separating us from other people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like trying to-- that-- for their-- you walk through, they know exactly what you are.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would do anything what they want to do with you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were worried, but they couldn't do anything about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You worry, but if you have something to do something about, you do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what are you going-- if there's nothing you can do help yourself, what are you going to do?",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
